Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:12.11,Default,8,500,0,0,,本次作戰的目的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:15.36,Default,8,0,0,0,,鎮壓這片被稱作大裂隙的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:20.61,Default,8,500,0,0,,目前第 4 次聯合中隊正在進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:23.00,Default,8,0,0,0,,但是由於叫龍的反擊　難以有所突破{sp：不確定原文}{攻めあぐねる}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:27.09,Default,8,0,0,0,,你們 13 部隊將與其他四個都市合流
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:30.13,Default,8,0,0,0,,結成第 6 次聯合中隊參加作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.42,Default,556,0,0,0,,那個「大裂隙」{Gran Crevasse}裡　到底有什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:40.97,Default,7,0,0,0,,這對你們幾個可能刺激有點大{$}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:45.23,Default,666,0,0,0,,什麼東西？黑色的...牆？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:48.95,Default,390,0,0,0,,這是什麼？到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.07,Default,214,0,0,0,,開玩笑吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:00:56.32,Default,556,0,0,0,,太慘了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:01:00.41,Default,326,0,0,0,,和迄今為止的戰鬥比起來　完全不是一個規模的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:05.04,Default,8,0,0,0,,對大裂隙的鎮壓　是爸爸長久以來的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.92,Default,8,0,0,0,,對於我們人類而言　這可以說是最重要的一場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:11.80,Default,56,0,0,0,,喂... 看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:26.31,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,果然啊　已經把他們全都吸乾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:28.44,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,這個野丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:30.25,Default,SageA,0,0,0,,終於要到最後關頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:34.71,Default,SageA,0,0,0,,對大裂隙的鎮壓一旦完成　我們夙願得償之時就不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:38.45,Default,SageB,0,0,0,,靈舡{Hringhorni}的建造也在穩步進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:42.33,Default,SageC,0,0,0,,等這兩邊都準備好了　就能讓它們回歸土地了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.58,Default,SageE,0,0,0,,時機已經到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:48.13,Default,Head,0,0,0,,你要去哪？ 韋納 {ウェルナー、ヴェルナー、ヴェルネル（Werner）は、ドイツ語圏の姓、男性名。北欧では Verner と書かれる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:50.16,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,這種地方我可待不住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:54.09,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,我要在特等席上　親眼見證到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:04.90,Default,16,0,0,0,,零貳...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:16.74,Default,090,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.61,Default,090,450,0,0,,敵人的數量太多了　我們的配合戰術用不起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:23.03,Default,090,0,0,0,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:27.20,Default,090,0,0,0,,等著！我現在馬上就...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:33.21,Default,090,0,0,0,,住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.82,Default,090,0,0,0,,剛才那個是...　鶴望蘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.42,Default,090,0,0,0,,怎　怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:52.43,Default,9a,0,0,120,,呀　真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:54.69,Default,9a,0,0,120,,對人類來說是很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.19,Default,PA,0,0,0,,作戰總部來電
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:04.45,Default,PA,0,0,0,,第 6 次聯合中隊　準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.32,Default,7,0,0,0,,各位　現在出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:11.42,Default,666,0,0,0,,好嘞　那我們就出去放倒叫龍去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.17,Default,214,0,0,0,,廣　可別偷吃我的飯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.83,Default,56,0,0,0,,別那麼一副陰暗的表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:23.36,Default,56,0,0,0,,有我們在就不會有問題　別瞎操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.30,Default,16,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:27.88,Default,15,0,0,0,,乖乖等著吧　廣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:32.81,Default,15,0,0,0,,等這場戰鬥結束了　我會從頭開始教你駕駛方法的{噗}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:39.19,Default,16,0,0,0,,大家　一定要平安回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.58,Default,7,0,0,0,,全機出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.92,Default,9c,0,0,0,,收拾你們連熱身都算不上！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.59,Default,9b,0,0,0,,不管來多少隻都是一樣　沒用沒用！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.66,Default,9d,0,0,0,,真沒勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:12.64,Default,9d,0,0,0,,多讓我們爽一爽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.00,Default,9a,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.41,Default,9a,0,0,0,,搞定{sp：敗了}{一丁上がり}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:27.91,Default,390,0,0,0,,好厲害！就像有好多台鶴望蘭一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.37,Default,15,0,0,0,,我們也上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.33,Default,9a,0,0,0,,這個數量倒確實有點超出想像了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.00,Default,9d,0,0,0,,沒完沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.63,Default,9b,0,0,0,,喂 α　看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.07,Default,9c,0,0,0,,那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.28,Default,9d,0,0,0,,是 13 部隊的孩子們呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.76,Default,9e,0,0,0,,α 所中意的部隊{sp：還是說人？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:48.27,Default,9a,0,0,0,,呀　這就是你的機體嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.80,Default,9a,0,0,0,,真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.06,Default,15,0,0,0,,那還真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.93,Default,15,0,0,0,,那　戰況呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:57.56,Default,9a,0,0,0,,雖說現在是死守住這裡　不過這樣下去也不會有進展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.98,Default,9a,0,0,0,,那個　你看得到的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.18,Default,9a,0,0,0,,那個巨穴被堅固的穹頂罩著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:06.71,Default,9a,0,0,0,,我們要突破那邊　就只能從內部攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.57,Default,9a,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.83,Default,15,0,0,0,,要從那邊過去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.68,Default,15,0,0,0,,上吧　各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:14.25,Default,15,0,0,0,,雞冠莧和金雀　跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.21,Default,15,0,0,0,,折鶴蘭　射擊掩護！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.46,Default,All,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.37,Default,196,0,0,0,,出全力上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:20.04,Default,214,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.82,Default,26A,0,0,0,,吶　那是在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.28,Default,26B,0,0,0,,那種戰鬥方法從來沒有見過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.41,Default,090,0,0,0,,是 13 部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.83,Default,090,0,0,0,,還是像以往一樣亂來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.85,Default,090,0,0,0,,真是振奮人心{真是鼓舞人心 //XXX怪}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.73,Default,090,0,0,0,,各位　趁現在重整隊形吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.54,Default,All,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.79,Default,556,0,0,0,,滿！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:55.99,Default,326,0,0,0,,我們上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:00.96,Default,56,0,0,0,,看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.95,Default,56,0,0,0,,是...人造物...嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.34,Default,15,0,0,0,,各位　我們從那裡衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.13,Default,666,0,0,0,,什　什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.84,Default,196,0,0,0,,叫龍們正在逃跑...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.60,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,哦？還藏著這種東西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.36,Default,7,0,0,0,,超雷曼級？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.94,Default,8,0,0,0,,連聽都沒聽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.54,Default,214,0,0,0,,山...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.41,Default,214,0,0,0,,山在動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.65,Default,090,0,0,0,,26 都市... 我們的都市被...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:11.66,Default,56,0,0,0,,糟了　它打算把種植園挨個摧毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:15.62,Default,PA,0,0,0,,超雷曼級叫龍從坐標 E3 開始移動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.83,Default,PA,0,0,0,,在預測路線上有三座種植園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.12,Default,ViceHead,0,0,0,,連線代號 090
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.75,Default,ViceHead,0,0,0,,執行 32 號方案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.30,Default,090,0,0,0,,32 號方案嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.76,Default,ViceHead,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.88,Default,090,0,0,0,,沒...沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.30,Default,ViceHead,0,0,0,,代號 090
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:34.05,Default,ViceHead,0,0,0,,這可是非常光榮的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.06,Default,090,0,0,0,,明白...了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.60,Default,PA,0,0,0,,超雷曼級正徑直向我們前進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.19,Default,PA,0,0,0,,距離抵達時間還有 240 秒
Comment: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{畫面}{算了，咕咕咕}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.69,Default,7,0,0,0,,這麼下去它會徑直撞上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:49.49,Default,326,0,0,0,,糟糕了　它衝著 13 都市去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.15,Default,666,0,0,0,,什...什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.78,Default,9a,0,0,0,,那麼　要怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:56.95,Default,9a,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.45,Default,9a,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:05.25,Default,090,0,0,0,,全機　32 號方案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.17,Default,All,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.72,Default,090,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:16.14,Default,090,0,0,0,,13 部隊　後面就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.06,Default,56,0,0,0,,怎...怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:27.19,Default,666,0,0,0,,停...停下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.48,Default,56,0,0,0,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.58,Default,214,0,0,0,,我...我們的都市被...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.25,Default,15,0,0,0,,各位　我們去保護它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.09,Default,All,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.63,Default,15,0,0,0,,零貳?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.79,Default,7,0,0,0,,關上隔離牆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.29,Default,7,0,0,0,,如果這裡失守了就都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.80,Default,8,0,0,0,,是的　最優先擊破那個超雷曼級
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:35.72,Default,7,0,0,0,,博士　這裡很危險　請回總部去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.22,Default,016,0,0,0,,廣也快回長青園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.72,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,你不覺得她遠比人類更加美麗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:46.23,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,驕傲而又純粹　比一切都更為孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.98,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,就像是叫龍本身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.86,Default,016,0,0,0,,不對　零貳才不是叫龍那種...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:10:00.12,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,我還以為這次說不定是找到搭檔了呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.62,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,真是個可憐姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.54,Default,214,0,0,0,,真是的　還要再打倒多少才行啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.88,Default,666,0,0,0,,別抱怨了　肥仔　得保護好我們的都市啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.13,Default,214,0,0,0,,別叫我肥仔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:13.00,Default,390,0,0,0,,我說　剛才那種光束再多射幾次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:16.59,Default,196,0,0,0,,沒有那份能量了　連備用的都用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.30,Default,390,0,0,0,,欸？小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.26,Default,556,0,0,0,,不能吵架　{金坷垃好處都有什麼}我們必須齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.65,Default,9b,0,0,0,,哇　好可怕　她今天心情不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.64,Default,9a,0,0,0,,要是與她為敵的話　想想都可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.28,Default,9a,0,0,0,,那種醜陋的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.53,Default,15,0,0,0,,零貳...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:49.87,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}零貳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.88,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個時候　你想說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:04.97,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.10,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在猶豫些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.27,Default,556,0,0,0,,叫龍入侵進來了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.44,Default,326,0,0,0,,不能再讓它們前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:18.99,Default,196,0,0,0,,彈藥耗盡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.82,Default,214,0,0,0,,沒有彈藥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.20,Default,214,0,0,0,,就只有靠蠻力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.95,Default,390,0,0,0,,等...等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.00,Default,666,0,0,0,,這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:35.17,Default,666,0,0,0,,怎麼能輸給你們　這個都市由我們來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.26,Default,56,0,0,0,,喂　莓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.01,Default,56,0,0,0,,莓　後面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.35,Default,56,0,0,0,,別分心　莓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.35,Default,15,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.85,Default,15,0,0,0,,什...什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.35,Default,15,0,0,0,,為什麼這種地方會有訓練機？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:53.98,Default,666,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:54.90,Default,666,0,0,0,,什麼...什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.11,Default,390,0,0,0,,欸...等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.61,Default,390,0,0,0,,難道是...廣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.82,Default,56,0,0,0,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:06.03,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從什麼時候開始　我不再想要尋求答案了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.37,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時我只是想要了解外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.83,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想從苗圃裡出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.34,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直都是孤獨的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.13,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}充斥著沒人在我身邊的　這種不安感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:21.72,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是　當我看見你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.05,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發現存有和我一樣對抗世界的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.68,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我無比地開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.65,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.07,Default,16,0,0,0,,沒有你...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.36,Default,16,0,0,0,,沒有你的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:43.95,Default,16,0,0,0,,我就沒辦法飛翔{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.54,Default,15,0,0,0,,廣　你為什麼到這裡來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.58,Default,15,0,0,0,,用這種訓練機　你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.42,Default,15,0,0,0,,我絕對不會放你走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.34,Default,15,0,0,0,,什...什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.80,Default,15,0,0,0,,我說... 五郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.17,Default,56,0,0,0,,夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.01,Default,15,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.30,Default,56,0,0,0,,這樣的廣和零貳　我真是看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.22,Default,56,0,0,0,,廣　進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.56,Default,56,0,0,0,,你有想要告訴她的話對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:18.02,Default,15,0,0,0,,莓　把廣帶到零貳那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.78,Default,15,0,0,0,,你也很擔心零貳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.45,Default,16,0,0,0,,抱歉　莓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.91,Default,15,0,0,0,,真的是麻煩死了　男男女女什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:34.79,Default,15,0,0,0,,要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.09,Default,15,0,0,0,,{\blur5}進來了　廣的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.68,Default,15,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.34,Default,15,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是廣的記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.51,Default,15,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住手　不要給我看這些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.39,Default,15,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好不容易和廣連接　但是這...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:58.06,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等著我　零貳{ep01}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.48,Default,16,0,0,0,,等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:04.65,Default,15,0,0,0,,贏不了啊　這顆心裡只有那一個人吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.99,Default,15,0,0,0,,我們上　廣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.37,Default,16,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.75,Default,56,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.00,Default,666,750,0,0,,你在裝什麼帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.00,Default,390,0,750,0,,你在裝什麼帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.77,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我本想變成人類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.60,Default,15,0,0,0,,零貳！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.27,Default,16,0,0,0,,莓...莓？為什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:46.61,Default,15,0,0,0,,混蛋　我已經受夠被你耍著玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.32,Default,16,0,0,0,,住手　莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.74,Default,15,0,0,0,,你這種人...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.21,Default,15,0,0,0,,從一開始就不存在該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:08.01,Default,15,0,0,0,,我把廣讓給你　所以你差不多該給我振作起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.19,Default,16,0,0,0,,是我　零貳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.07,Default,16,0,0,0,,我來見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.15,Default,15,0,0,0,,保護好鶴望蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:31.66,Default,15,0,0,0,,雖然不甘心　但是只有鶴望蘭才能打倒那個大傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.16,Default,556,0,0,0,,叫龍的數量也減少了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.71,Default,326,0,0,0,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.96,Default,390,0,0,0,,我第一次打倒這麼多叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.79,Default,666,0,0,0,,喂　未來　有什麼東西掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.09,Default,390,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.51,Default,196,0,0,0,,看起來像是人類啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.05,Default,390,0,0,0,,啊？別亂說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.14,Default,214,0,0,0,,對...對啊　這怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.64,Default,326,0,0,0,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.77,Default,326,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:07.78,Default,PA,0,0,0,,第 37 種植園　備份作業已完成 98% {是…是人格上傳}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.28,Default,Head,0,0,0,,讓他們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:14.20,Default,Head,0,0,0,,把他們從肉體的牢籠中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.75,Default,666,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.59,Default,214,0,0,0,,還...還有大人在裡面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:28.38,Default,326,0,0,0,,難道他們要讓都市自爆嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.30,Default,9e,0,0,0,,開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:34.80,Default,9a,0,0,0,,看起來爸爸是想在不靠鶴望蘭的情況下解決
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.56,Default,9b,0,0,0,,還會犧牲掉幾個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.56,Default,8,0,0,0,,要做到這一步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.56,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,愚蠢...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.82,Default,16,0,0,0,,果然沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.36,Default,16,0,0,0,,這樣的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:53.57,Default,16,0,0,0,,抱歉　讓我摸一下{我要摸你（扶額）}{sp：不是你，是角吧}　零貳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:57.08,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了　再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.33,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再一次帶我到你那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.46,Default,ResA,0,0,0,,代號 016 的記憶調整已結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:09.05,Default,ResA,0,0,0,,但是 002 有些區域無法更改
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.84,Default,ResA,0,0,0,,就好像有什麼強力的東西在起作用一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:14.22,Default,ResB,0,0,0,,把記憶消除掉　讓它們變成噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.43,Default,ResC,0,0,0,,但是連續使用會帶來太大的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.35,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.81,Default,ResB,0,0,0,,代號 016 要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.10,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,帶他回苗圃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.81,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,混入了她的血液　他大概已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.11,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,但是作為實驗體來說很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.09,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:04.48,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是忘了的話　我就不會再變成人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:15.15,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我學會的第一個詞語是「我」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.16,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第二個詞是「零貳」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.33,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後　第三個詞是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.83,Default,16,0,0,0,,然後我就會成為你的 Darling 了{ep13}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.38,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「Darling」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:39.84,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Dali!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.06,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你一直都沒有忘記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.69,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,我好像對你有點興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.65,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,要不要來做我的 Darling 呢？{ep01}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.31,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,現在起你就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.82,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,我的 Darling！{ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.94,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即使被傷得這麼深
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:19:00.24,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也要獨自一人與這世界對抗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.96,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,D...Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.92,Default,16,0,0,0,,終於見到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.21,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,不...不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.47,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,你不怕我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.34,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,我可是利用了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.22,Default,16,0,0,0,,那已經沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:29.02,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,但是... 但是我把你稱作飼料...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.90,Default,16,0,0,0,,我也說過你是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.65,Default,16,0,0,0,,所以這就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:37.19,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,沒錯　我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.03,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,所以說...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.70,Default,16,0,0,0,,不是的　我們要好好說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.37,Default,16,0,0,0,,我們必須要想清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.87,Default,16,0,0,0,,我們肯定找得到出路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.50,Default,16,0,0,0,,我們就從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:52.38,Default,16,0,0,0,,這個世界肯定比我們所想像的更大更廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.38,Default,16,0,0,0,,在那時沒能做到　但是這次...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.38,Default,16,0,0,0,,我們兩人一起去看看外面的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.80,Default,16,0,0,0,,零貳...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.43,Default,16,0,0,0,,我們是兩人一體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.31,Default,390,0,0,0,,還沒搞定嗎　廣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.82,Default,214,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:17.07,Default,15,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.49,Default,556,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.49,Default,15,0,0,0,,那道光...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.08,Default,7,0,0,0,,博士...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.45,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,他做到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.84,Default,All,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.34,Default,16,0,0,0,,零貳！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.05,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.55,Default,16,0,0,0,,零貳！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.47,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.26,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.22,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.52,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.36,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.78,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,我能遇到你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.86,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,我超喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.37,Default,16,0,0,0,,零貳　我也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.25,Default,16,0,0,0,,我超喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.92,Default,666,0,0,0,,笨蛋　把通訊斷開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:18.59,Default,214,0,0,0,,是啊　是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.30,Default,390,0,0,0,,真是兩個笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:24.63,Default,15,0,0,0,,太好了　你們兩個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.72,Default,16,0,0,0,,零貳　那個穹頂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.72,Default,16,0,0,0,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.27,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,當然啦　要是和 Darling 一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.81,Default,9a,0,0,0,,那我們也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:47.12,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.38,Default,9a,0,0,0,,差不多是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.13,Default,9a,0,0,0,,動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:04.97,Default,All,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:24.24,Default,556,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:29.99,Default,ViceHead,0,0,0,,這樣通往大裂隙{}的門扉就被打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:34.16,Default,Head,0,0,0,,終於　人類解放之日近了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:38.04,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像是被稱作「比翼鳥」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:42.21,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種鳥只有一邊的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:45.80,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果不是雄性和雌性靠在一起行動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:48.76,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就沒辦法飛上天　是一種不完全的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.55,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:51.55,Default,Z2,0,650,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:52.47,Default,16,650,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:54.27,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卻覺得這種生命的存在方式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:58.14,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,{\blur5}十分地美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:05.78,Default,9d,0,0,0,,吶　看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:09.78,Default,9e,0,0,0,,不會這麼簡單地結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:12.24,Default,9c,0,0,0,,核心複合體？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:14.08,Default,9b,0,0,0,,這也真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.87,Default,9a,0,0,0,,已經趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:19.79,Default,9a,0,0,0,,在這一帶被碾碎前　我們先撤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.67,Default,16,0,0,0,,零貳　我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:22.29,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:33.01,Default,9a,0,0,0,,馬上就有反應了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:53.78,Default,56,0,0,0,,逃...逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.58,Default,196,0,0,0,,但是　那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:58.12,Default,15,0,0,0,,超大的手？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:58.97,Default-Top,9a,0,0,1,,剩下的我們會處理的　你們就在後面隨便應付{摸摸魚}吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:05.95,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.29,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,第 6 次聯合中隊　準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.32,Default-Top,7,0,0,0,,目標 F2 地點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.45,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,確認到地下岩漿能量活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.19,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,重新測定振動波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.60,Default-Top,PA,0,0,0,,判定為「超雷曼級」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.67,Default-Top,8,0,0,0,,大裂隙{}會由爸爸們來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.84,Default-Top,Z2,0,650,0,,要不要來做我的 Darling 呢{ep01}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.55,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,你很棒哦{ep02}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.34,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,很簡單吧{ep03}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:46.96,Default-Top,Z2,0,650,0,,你想乘上我？{ep3}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.64,Default-Top,Z2,0,650,0,,我可以帶 Darling 你從這裡離開{ep03}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.60,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,要放棄的話就趁現在哦{ep04}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.72,Default-Top,Z2,0,650,0,,當然是消滅怪物啊{ep01}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.52,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,其實你也覺得我是一個怪物嗎?{ep04}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.39,Default-Top,Z2,650,0,0,,畢竟你只是我的飼料罷了{ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.73,Default-Top,Z2,0,0,0,,現在起你就是...{ep01}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.15,Default-Top,Z2,0,0,0,,我的 Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:25.83,Default-Top,Sign,0,0,0,,...千萬不要離開我哦，Darling」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:29.91,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,そばに来て　崩れゆく抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:34.88,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ボクを怖がらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:53.06,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,飛べない鳥が　夢見た空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:59.90,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,交わってく色　それは違う Red
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:08.12,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ドアを叩く音に　ボクは耳を塞いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:15.33,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,叩いてるのはキミ？それとも他の？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:21.30,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,Will your lips taste the kiss of death？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:28.89,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ダーリン運命が血管を走るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:35.98,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,動き始めた世界 ...愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:44.53,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,誰よりも溶け合いたいよダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:49.83,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ボクを怖がらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.66,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,Kiss me now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:58.00,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,死は逝くときと似た
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:05.80,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,感覚とキミの味がした
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:12.68,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,Did your lips taste the kiss of death？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:23.90,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ダーリン運命が血管を走るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:31.16,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,動き始めた世界 ...愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.04,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,誰よりも溶け合いたいよダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:44.76,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,ボクを怖がらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:52.43,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,キミを味あわせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:55.68,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,Kiss me now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:29.91,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,到我身邊來　抑制即將崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:34.88,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,請你不要懼怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:53.06,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,無法飛翔的鳥　所夢見的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:59.90,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,相交在一起的顏色　那是別樣的殷紅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:08.12,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,敲叩門扉的聲音　我堵住耳朵不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:15.33,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,那敲門的是你　還是另有他人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:21.30,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,你的雙唇是否願意品嘗死亡之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:28.89,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,Darling 命運在血管中奔湧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:35.98,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,世界運轉起來　還有愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:44.53,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,我只想與你身心交融 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:49.83,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,請你不要懼怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.66,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,Kiss me now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:58.00,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,就像嚐到了瀕死一般...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:05.80,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,的感覺和你的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:12.68,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,你的雙唇是否已經品嚐過死亡之吻
